        "content": "<p>I've reduced <code>metric_carleson</code> to one final lemma, <code>BST_LNT_of_BST_NT</code> in my PR, and I have two sorries in that lemma – measurability of <code>linearizedNontangentialOperator</code> and the above goal. I will gladly accept any help with these two sorries :)</p>",
